    S --- UC24 & UC25

    O --- UC1 & UC2 & UC3 & UC4 & UC5 & UC6 & UC7
    O --- UC8 & UC9 & UC10 & UC11
    O --- UC12 & UC13 & UC14 & UC15
    O --- UC20 & UC21 & UC22 & UC23
    O --- UC24 & UC25
